# Project context

This is a **HubSpot CMS** project (CMS React theme, HubL templates, and `fields.json`).

## Active project

- **Current project**: `landing-pages-v1` (repo root).
- **Theme source**: `src/theme/landing-page-theme/`
- Default all reads, edits, search, grep, and terminal work to this repo unless the user says otherwise.

## Workspace sibling (reference only)

The workspace may also include `cms-elevate-theme-public` (Elevate theme reference).

- **Do not** search, grep, read, or copy from that folder unless the user explicitly asks (e.g. “check Elevate”, “look in cms-elevate-theme-public”).
- When asked, use it as reference only; implement changes in `landing-pages-v1`.

## Common paths

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| React modules | `src/theme/landing-page-theme/components/modules/` |
| Field library | `src/theme/landing-page-theme/components/fieldLibrary/` |
| Shared utils | `src/theme/landing-page-theme/components/utils/` |
| Theme fields | `src/theme/landing-page-theme/fields.json` |
| HubL templates | `src/theme/landing-page-theme/templates/` |

## Commands

- Theme dev server: `npm start` from `src/theme/landing-page-theme/`
- Project upload: `npm run upload` or `hs project upload` from repo root
- Tests: `npm test` from repo root (Vitest)
